Automatically remove saved ideas when a script is successfully built from them

Add `ideaId` to `PrefillData` interface and use it in `ArcScriptBuilderTool.handleSave` to delete the idea from saved if it exists. Update `IdeaCard.handleBuildScript` to include `ideaId` in sessionStorage when building a script from a saved idea.

